    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338800/extras/bb3f9e9ae9330054f67e74e60817495f.avif?t=1714352248\" width=600 height=176 /></span><br><br>《天台物语》是一款可以种植庄稼、饲养动物、与NPC增进关系的模拟经营类游戏。<br>与其他农场类游戏不同的是，本作的故事发生在一个城市小区当中。<br>当疫情来袭，小区进入<strong>为期一个月</strong>的封控状态。作为一名社区志愿者，面对物资短缺，你会怎么办？<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种植蔬菜或水果</h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338800/extras/ac69587c42cc830d9be3f338d1a408f3.avif?t=1714352248\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><i>在天台菜园里种植蔬菜或水果。<br>通过精心照料，等待农作物成熟之后出售或者制作菜肴！</i><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >饲养牲畜</h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338800/extras/fe8e6f61fcfa9dae1c480eab5b270f72.avif?t=1714352248\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><i>在天台设施内饲养小鸡、养殖水产。<br>经过用心喂养，育成的动物们会持续产出蛋和肉！</i><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >采集与垂钓</h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338800/extras/094da08369d485c1ac183c65a55d80bc.avif?t=1714352248\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><i>在小区绿地里寻找种类丰富的野菜；在景观池当中进行垂钓，获得新鲜的鱼虾！</i><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加工与保存食物</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338800/extras/b1fa267d1a58f644133cff4700869383.avif?t=1714352248\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><br><i>将食材用传统方法进行腌制、风干、酿造，制作出各种风味美食。</i><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >增进关系</h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338800/extras/932f2a622399699d49bc984c7d110ac4.avif?t=1714352248\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><br><i>满足居民们千奇百怪的需求吧！<br>当你们的关系加深时可以解锁游戏中各项设施，并获得能力提升。</i><br><br><br>疫情终将过去，保持乐观心态，与小区居民同心协力、共度时艰。",
